    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. Validation results for pressure-flow curve, relative hemolysis index, and wall shear stress demonstrate adequate model credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The CFD model is accepted as fit for the stated COU: supporting regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device with RH < 1 acceptance criterion.",
